    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Marshal Dedication]</p>\n<p>You and your allies within the aura gain a +1 status bonus to saving throws against fear.</p>\n<p>If you're in @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Devrin's Cunning Stance], you and your allies gain a +1 status bonus to skill checks. When you or an ally in the aura Strike an @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] enemy, that enemy can't use reactions until the beginning of its next turn.</p>\n<p>If you're in @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Dread Marshal Stance], you and your allies in the aura gain a status bonus to damage rolls equal to your weapon's number of damage dice. When you or an ally in the aura critically hit an enemy with a Strike, that enemy is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p>If you're in @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.Inspiring Marshal Stance], you and your allies gain a +1 status bonus to attack rolls and saves against mental effects.</p>"
        },
